# ChronoQuest: Fractures in Time - Technical Documentation

## Project Overview

ChronoQuest is a time-travel puzzle adventure game developed for the BPA (Business 
Professionals of America) Software Engineering Team (Vo3) competition. Built entirely 
in Python with zero external dependencies, the game demonstrates professional software 
engineering practices including OOP, error handling, persistence, and comprehensive 
documentation.

## Quick Start

### Installation
```bash
python main.py       # Windows
python3 main.py      # macOS/Linux
```

### Game Features
- 4 Unique historical eras
- 4 Interactive puzzles
- Save/Load functionality
- Health system
- Inventory management
- NPC interaction
- Timeline tracking

